<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>PDF on Alejandro U. Alvarez</title><link>https://aurbano.eu/tags/PDF/</link><description>Recent content in PDF on Alejandro U. Alvarez</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Jun 2016 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aurbano.eu/tags/PDF/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Generating Pixel Perfect PDF Reports</title><link>https://aurbano.eu/post/2016-06-21-generating-pdf-reports/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jun 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aurbano.eu/post/2016-06-21-generating-pdf-reports/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Have you been tasked with generating PDF reports? If you have tried using the typical tools (iText for Java, ReportLab in Python&amp;hellip; ) you understand why it&amp;rsquo;s bad.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Imagine having to build a PDF like this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rectangle pagesize &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Rectangle(216f, 720f);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Document document &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Document(pagesize, 36f, 72f, 108f, 180f);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// step 2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;PdfWriter.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getInstance&lt;/span&gt;(document, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; FileOutputStream(RESULT));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// step 3&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;document.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;open&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// step 4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;document.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Paragraph(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello World! Hello People! &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello Sky! Hello Sun! Hello Moon! Hello Stars!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// step 5&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;document.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;close&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now add images, charts&amp;hellip; and get ready to quit your job and become a farmer.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>